title: Keith Jarrett - Death and the Flower (1975 quad mix 24/96 lossle
description:
Keith Jarrett - Death and the Flower (1975 quad mix 24/96 lossless 4.0 DVD-A)

24/96 4.0 lossless MLP (DVD-Audio).
16/48 4.0 AC3 @ 440kbps (DVD-Video) for compatibility with standard DVD players.
Slight noise/crackle filtering applied (Izotope RX 2), no EQ, compression, or rear channel boost.

Converted from quad QS encoded vinyl using a SANSUI QS-D1000 VARIO MATRIX hardware decoder.



"Jarrett has the kind of gift that is labeled genius because it's so hard to put down. But for a genius, he makes an awful lot of music that can best be described as pleasant. Granted that its pleasantness is substantial and sensual and spirited all at once. Granted too that the accomplishment of this album is more reliable than that of his last group effort, Treasure Island. I still expect more from a genius." B
- Robert Christgau, Village Voice
